Documentation folder for the LM project
	Folders:
		'draft_xx'   =   development code  (testing and prototyping goes here)
		'LM_xxx'		 =		functional code
		'LM_doc'		=	This folder with documentation, todo lists etc.


Coding style - see https://docs.google.com/document/d/1D1KMGvOP9Qnw67Gu55Kmd1BUy42NN0EjFfKc5rkeJU8


